        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "The implementation of Zend_Filter_StripTags fails on the next code (similar to issue ZF-8894):\r\n\r\n{noformat}\r\n$value = 'test <!-- testcomment --> test <div>div-content<\/div>';\r\n\r\n$stripTags = new Zend_Filter_StripTags();    \r\n$string = $stripTags->filter($value); \r\n{noformat}\r\n\r\nThe expected result is \"test test <div>div-content<\/div>\" but an empty string is returned.\r\n\r\nThe error generates on this line of the Zend_Filter_StripTags implementation:\r\n\r\n{noformat}\r\n$value = 'test <!-- testcomment --> test <div>div-content<\/div>';\r\n$valueCopy = preg_replace('#<!--(?:[^<]+|<(?!\\!--))*?(--\\s*>)#s', '', (string) $value);\r\nZend_Debug::dump($valueCopy);    \r\nswitch (preg_last_error()) {\r\n    case PREG_NO_ERROR:\r\n        print \"pcre_error: PREG_NO_ERROR!\\n\";\r\n        break;\r\n    case PREG_INTERNAL_ERROR:\r\n        print \"pcre_error: PREG_INTERNAL_ERROR!\\n\";\r\n        break;\r\n    case PREG_BACKTRACK_LIMIT_ERROR:\r\n        print \"pcre_error: PREG_BACKTRACK_LIMIT_ERROR!\\n\";\r\n        break;\r\n    case PREG_RECURSION_LIMIT_ERROR:\r\n        print \"pcre_error: PREG_RECURSION_LIMIT_ERROR!\\n\";\r\n        break;\r\n    case PREG_BAD_UTF8_ERROR:\r\n        print \"pcre_error: PREG_BAD_UTF8_ERROR!\\n\";\r\n        break;\r\n    case PREG_BAD_UTF8_OFFSET_ERROR:\r\n        print \"pcre_error: PREG_BAD_UTF8_OFFSET_ERROR!\\n\";\r\n        break;\r\n}\r\n{noformat} \r\n\r\npreg_replace returns null. preg_last_error() returns PREG_NO_ERROR.\r\n"
        },
